-reunion-dream-setlist-3788142">在这里查看<em>NME</em>即将举行的大型演出的梦想曲目表</a>。</p><p>还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-oasis-about-to-record-a-new-album-fans-have-some-theories-3788575">传言称绿洲乐队可能会推出新专辑</a>，并且目前正在“计划” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-plans-underway-for-2025-shows-outside-of-europe-3787647">在欧洲以外举办更多音乐会</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3787542" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3787542" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3787542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg" alt="Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，在 2025 年联合 Oasis 进行英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演。图片来源：Simon Emmett" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3787542" class="wp-caption-text"> Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，在 2025 年联合 Oasis 进行英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演。图片来源：Simon Emmett</figcaption></figure><p>此前有报道称，重新组合的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-oasis-reuniting-for-huge-london-and-manchester-shows-3786823">绿洲乐队可能会在温布利球场破纪录地连续演出 10 晚</a>，这将超过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> ) 最近在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-edinburgh-3763814">“Eras 巡回演唱会”</a>中在该场馆连续演出 8 晚的记录。在撰写本文时，加拉格尔夫妇计划明年在首都演出五个晚上。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-will-reportedly-make-more-than-400million-3787259">据报道，《Oasis Live &#39;25》的票房收入将达到令人瞠目结舌的 4 亿英镑</a>，并将紧随昨天（8 月 30 日星期五）发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念再版延长版</a>。</p><p>乐队还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-unveil-exclusive-merchandise-ahead-of-reunion-3789300">巡演前公布了一些新商品的细节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">绿洲乐队 2025 年重聚后：数十万粉丝在 Ticketmaster 上排起长队，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，这让粉丝们感到沮丧。</p> ;
